name: Delaware
absentee_method: Released as a separate subtotal as first report of the night
poll_display_race: Polls close at 7:30 p.m. Eastern time.
expectations_text_race: Postmarked ballots have until Nov. 13 to arrive, but no additional results will be reported reported for at least a week and a half after the election. Counties may report their full official count after their vote canvass, due by Nov. 18, but full statewide results will not be available until final certification, due by Nov. 28.
